flowchart TD
    START([Start analysis request])

    A1[Load candidate metadata from DB]
    A2[Load candidate files from object storage]
    A3[Load current job description]
    A4[Create workflow run record]

    B1[Document normalization<br/>parse CV transcripts notes]
    B2[Chunking + metadata extraction]
    B3[Index chunks into vector storage]

    C1[Job Description Agent<br/>extract rubric]
    C2[Candidate Extraction Agent<br/>extract skills experience education domain signals]
    C3[Interview Insight Agent<br/>summarize interview signals communication risks strengths]
    C4[Consistency Agent<br/>detect contradictions gaps suspicious timeline issues]
    C5[Evidence Retrieval Agent<br/>map claims to supporting evidence]
    C6[Background Check Agent<br/>separate policy-controlled branch]

    D1[Fact consolidation layer<br/>merge agent outputs]
    D2[Schema validation / confidence checks]
    D3[Human review required?]

    E1[Deterministic scoring engine]
    E2[Recommendation engine<br/>strong match / possible / weak / manual review]

    F1[Report Drafting Agent]
    F2[Report Verification Agent<br/>unsupported claims completeness tone]
    F3[Render HTML]
    F4[Generate PDF]
    F5[Store PDF and report snapshot]

    END([Completed])

    START --> A1 --> A2 --> A3 --> A4
    A4 --> B1 --> B2 --> B3

    B3 --> C1
    B3 --> C2
    B3 --> C3
    B3 --> C4
    B3 --> C5
    B3 --> C6

    C1 --> D1
    C2 --> D1
    C3 --> D1
    C4 --> D1
    C5 --> D1
    C6 --> D1

    D1 --> D2 --> D3
    D3 -->|No| E1
    D3 -->|Yes| E2

    E1 --> E2
    E2 --> F1 --> F2 --> F3 --> F4 --> F5 --> END